  "detailed_description": "Take on the role of commander of a remote space outpost. <br><br>Hire pilots, each with their own personality (Hunter, support, defender, etc.) and differently suited to the task.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820020/extras/e042cc8937b94611bc363ea28b9aa67b.poster.avif?t=1745528154\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820020/extras/e042cc8937b94611bc363ea28b9aa67b.webm?t=1745528154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820020/extras/e042cc8937b94611bc363ea28b9aa67b.mp4?t=1745528154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Research new modules to find the perfect combination<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820020/extras/8b101d3f8b6bbd4e7f52c4092ad584de.poster.avif?t=1745528154\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820020/extras/8b101d3f8b6bbd4e7f52c4092ad584de.webm?t=1745528154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820020/extras/8b101d3f8b6bbd4e7f52c4092ad584de.mp4?t=1745528154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Build and develop the base, gaining access to more advanced technologists for your rangers to use. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820020/extras/3a6bdacccdbe9bd6bf59e5f7baefb9d4.poster.avif?t=1745528154\" width=600 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820020/extras/3a6bdacccdbe9bd6bf59e5f7baefb9d4.webm?t=1745528154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820020/extras/3a6bdacccdbe9bd6bf59e5f7baefb9d4.mp4?t=1745528154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Develop your economy by trading with neighboring areas and don't forget to guard your merchant ships.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820020/extras/dacf02215e333b85a85099fd6f13c0ee.poster.avif?t=1745528154\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820020/extras/dacf02215e333b85a85099fd6f13c0ee.webm?t=1745528154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820020/extras/dacf02215e333b85a85099fd6f13c0ee.mp4?t=1745528154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Many different ships with their own weapons and support modules.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820020/extras/b1c276f44d4dffba0defe7dfb07de486.poster.avif?t=1745528154\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820020/extras/b1c276f44d4dffba0defe7dfb07de486.webm?t=1745528154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820020/extras/b1c276f44d4dffba0defe7dfb07de486.mp4?t=1745528154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
